Grammar!


Syntax: listen (http|https|redirect) (address) (port)
Ex: listen https 10.0.0.12 443
Ex: listen redirect [2001:db8::1:0:0:1] 1009

Syntax: httpscert (key path) (cert path)
Ex: httpscert "/var/lib/root.key" "/var/lib/root.cert"

Syntax: hostacl (path)
Ex: hostacl "/var/lib/hostrules.txt"

Syntax: pathacl (path)
Ex: pathacl "/var/lib/easylists.txt"

Syntax: allowlocalhost (on|off)
Ex: allowlocalhost off

Syntax: loopDetection (on|off)
Ex: loopdetection on

Syntax: staticsite (host) (directory)
Ex: staticsite "adsieve" "/var/www"

Syntax: staticsitecert (host) (key path) (cert path)

Syntax: # <Anything>
Ex: #This is a comment
